#!/usr/bin/perl

use warnings;
use centreon::script::centcore;

centreon::script::centcore->new()->run();

__END__

=head1 NAME

centcore - a daemon to manage pollers.

=head1 SYNOPSIS

centcore [options]

=head1 OPTIONS

=over 8

=item B<--config>

Specify the path to the main configuration file (default: /etc/centreon/centreon-config.pm).

=item B<--help>

Print a brief help message and exits.

=back

=head1 DESCRIPTION

B<centcore> manage pollers: push configurations, send commands, get perfdata/logs (if ndoutils).

=cut

